<xml>
 
  </xml><ul type="discd"><li>Crossing
     the Hampta Pass and entering the starkly different landscapes of Lahaul
     and Spiti</li>
 <li>Scenic
     views of snow-clad peaks, alpine meadows, and lush green valleys</li>
 <li>Camping
     beside the beautiful Chandra Tal Lake</li>
 <li>Trekking
     through dense pine and oak forests</li>
 <li>Panoramic
     views from the top of Hampta Pass</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM">&nbsp;</p>


<br /></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>Are there any cultural or historical aspects of the trek?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>The trek provides an opportunity to explore the local culture of the Himachali people. You may pass through remote villages and get a glimpse of their traditional lifestyle and customs.<br /></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>What kind of fitness is required for the trek?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>A good level of fitness is required for the Hampta Pass trek. Regular cardiovascular exercise, such as jogging, swimming, or cycling, and leg strengthening exercises can help prepare for the trek.<br /></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
                                                            <div class="detailfaq-item">
                                 <button class="detailfaq-question">
                                 <span>What should I be aware of regarding altitude sickness?</span>
                                 <span class="detailfaq-icon">▼</span>
                                 </button>
                                 <div class="detailfaq-answer">
                                    <p>


<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<meta name="ProgId" content="Word.DocumentW" />
<meta name="Generator" content="Microsoft Word 15" />
