<xml>
 
  </xml><p class="MsoNormalM">Altitude sickness can affect anyone above 2,500 meters. To
minimize the risk:</p>

<ul type="discd">
 <li>Acclimatize
     properly</li>
 <li>Stay
     hydrated</li>
 <li>Avoid
     alcohol and smoking</li>
 <li>Ascend
     slowly and give your body time to adjust</li>
</ul>

<p class="MsoNormalM">This FAQ should provide a thorough overview for anyone
considering the Hampta Pass trek. If you have more specific questions, feel
free to ask!</p></p>                                 </div>
                              </div>
